== 上映 ==

[[華特迪士尼工作室電影|華特迪士尼工作室電影]]最初選定的上映日期為2016年4月15日，接著提前至2015年10月9日<ref>{{cite news |last1=McNary |first1=Dave |title=Disney Sets Several 2016 Release Dates |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/disney-sets-several-2016-release-dates-1201404285/ |accessdate=2015-01-14 |newspaper=Variety |date=2015-01-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114043027/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/disney-sets-several-2016-release-dates-1201404285/ |archivedate=2015-01-14 }}</ref>，最終定於2016年1月29日在美國上映<ref name="NewDate"/>。首支[[預告片|預告片]]於2015年7月8日釋出<ref>{{cite news|last1=Petski|first1=Denise|title=‘The Finest Hours’ Trailer: Chris Pine At The Helm Of Harrowing Rescue Mission|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/the-finest-hours-trailer-disney-chris-pine-casey-affleck-1201472152/|accessdate=2015-07-08|work=Deadline|date=2015-07-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709071753/http://deadline.com/2015/07/the-finest-hours-trailer-disney-chris-pine-casey-affleck-1201472152/|archivedate=2015-07-09}}</ref>。第二支預告片在11月11日發布<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Watch: Chris Pine Braves the Waves in ‘Finest Hours’ Trailer|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/the-finest-hours-trailer-chris-pine-1201638842/|accessdate=2015-11-13|work=Variety|date=2015-11-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113083818/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/the-finest-hours-trailer-chris-pine-1201638842/|archivedate=2015-11-13}}</ref>。《絕命救援》於2016年1月15日在科羅納多島電影節（{{lang|en|Coronado Island Film Festival}}）首次亮相<ref>{{cite news|last1=Galuppo|first1=Mia|title=Coronado Island Film Festival Unveils Opening, Closing Night Screenings|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/coronado-island-film-festival-unveils-849181|accessdate=2015-12-16|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-12-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222142532/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/coronado-island-film-festival-unveils-849181|archivedate=2015-12-22}}</ref>。全球[[首映|首映]]禮於1月25日在美國加利福尼亞州[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]的[[中國戲院|中國戲院]]舉行<ref>{{cite news|last1=Emery|first1=Debbie|title=Chris Pine, Casey Affleck, Eric Bana Honor US Coast Guard at ‘Finest Hours’ Premiere|url=http://www.thewrap.com/chris-pine-casey-affleck-erin-bana-honor-us-coast-guard-at-finest-hours-premiere-photos/|accessdate=2016-01-28|work=The Wrap|date=2016-01-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201040517/http://www.thewrap.com/chris-pine-casey-affleck-erin-bana-honor-us-coast-guard-at-finest-hours-premiere-photos/|archivedate=2016-02-01}}</ref>。電影的[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]及[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]於5月24日發布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/7180/the-finest-hours |title=The Finest Hours (2016) |publisher=DVDsReleaseDates.com |date= |accessdate=2016-05-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527190040/http://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/7180/the-finest-hours |archivedate=2016-05-27 }}</ref>。

== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===

《絕命救援》所獲評價整題而言褒貶不一。[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的171篇專業影評文章中，有108篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為63%，平均得分6.1分（滿分10分），該網站對電影的共識性評價寫道「《絕命救援》所具備的老式故事，將滿足那些追求傳統救援劇情片的觀眾——但可能會讓部分熱愛冒險片的觀眾渴求更多」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_finest_hours/ |title=The Finest Hours (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-07-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611051558/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_finest_hours |archivedate=2016-06-11 }}</ref>，而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的39篇評論文章，其中18篇予以好評，無差評，21篇褒貶不一，平均分為58（滿分100），綜合結果為「混合或中等評價」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-finest-hours |title=The Finest Hours |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-02-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160212083711/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-finest-hours |archivedate=2016-02-12 }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A-」<ref name="box office" />。

部分影評人對電影抱持積極的評價。《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》的凱特·泰勒（{{lang|en|Kate Taylor}}）給予3顆星（滿分4顆）的評價，寫道「《絕命救援》沒什麼奧妙之處，但許多部份令人滿意」<ref>{{cite web |last=Taylor |first=Kate |title=The Finest Hours: Coast Guard heroism film rides one fierce roller after another |work=The Globe and Mail |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/film-reviews/the-finest-hours-coast-guard-heroism-film-rides-one-fierce-roller-after-another/article28438578/ |accessdate=2016-01-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129062423/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/film/film-reviews/the-finest-hours-coast-guard-heroism-film-rides-one-fierce-roller-after-another/article28438578/ |archivedate=2016-01-29 }}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的瑞安·吉爾比（{{lang|en|Ryan Gilbey}}）給出了3顆星（滿分5顆），稱「你必須同意伯尼需要一艘更大的船。指南針也就不會失去。不過這部樸實無華的劇情片了解如何真實的呈現」<ref>{{cite web |last=Gilbey |first=Ryan |title=The Finest Hours review – Chris Pine saves the day the old-fashioned way |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/feb/18/the-finest-hours-review-chris-pine-disney-holliday-grainger |date=2016-02-18 |accessdate=2016-02-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219002422/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/feb/18/the-finest-hours-review-chris-pine-disney-holliday-grainger |archivedate=2016-02-19 }}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{link-en|史蒂芬·霍登|Stephen Holden}}表示「《絕命救援》從未試圖脫離確切的公式，但那就是它古雅的魅力之一」<ref>{{cite web |last=Holden |first=Stephen |title=Review: ‘The Finest Hours’ Stars Chris Pine, Leading a Mission Against All Odds |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/29/movies/chris-pine-the-finest-hours-review.html?partner=rss&emc=rss&_r=0 |date=2016-01-28 |accessdate=2016-01-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021060455/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/29/movies/chris-pine-the-finest-hours-review.html?partner=rss&emc=rss&_r=0 |archivedate=2017-10-21 }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的{{link-en|麥可·菲利浦斯|Michael Phillips}}給予電影的評分為3顆星（滿分4顆），並寫道「該劇本完整採用某些角色原型（豬頭的船員隊友、嚴厲的長官），但並沒有完全成功。然而，語調、畫面的情緒以及不飽和的調色，維持了正確的氣氛」<ref>{{cite web | last = Phillips | first = Michael | title = 'The Finest Hours' review: Casey Affleck, Chris Pine star in suspenseful Coast Guard rescue | work = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | url = http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/sc-mov-0126-finest-hours-rev-20160126-column.html | accessdate = 2016-01-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160127154319/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/sc-mov-0126-finest-hours-rev-20160126-column.html | archivedate = 2016-01-27 }}</ref>。

然而評論中也不乏批評的聲音。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的{{link-en|理察·羅珀|Richard Roeper}}給出了2顆星（滿分4顆），表示「1952年那艘小艇隊員的英勇表現值得拍攝成一部特別的電影，但不是這一部」<ref>{{cite web | last = Roeper | first = Richard | title = Review: ‘The Finest Hours’: Rescuers heroic, but the script is all wet | work = The Chicago Sun-Times | url = http://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/the-finest-hours-rescuers-heroic-but-the-script-is-all-wet/ | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305194702/http://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/the-finest-hours-rescuers-heroic-but-the-script-is-all-wet/ | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。{{link-en|Vox (網站)|Vox (website)|Vox}}的陶德·范德韋爾夫（{{lang|en|Todd VanDerWerff}}）稱「彭德爾頓船上的一切是該片唯一引人注目的部分——而它僅占用了片長的3分之1」<ref>{{cite web | last = VanDerWerff | first = Todd | title = The Finest Hours is mostly Chris Pine going up and over giant waves in a tiny boat | work = Vox | url = http://www.vox.com/2016/1/29/10867096/the-finest-hours-review-disney | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130084335/http://www.vox.com/2016/1/29/10867096/the-finest-hours-review-disney | archivedate = 2016-01-30 }}</ref>。《論壇新聞服務》的凱蒂·華許（{{lang|en|Katie Walsh}}）的評分為2顆星（滿分4顆），認為該片「感覺就像是對一部知名電影所做的拙劣模仿」，且「類似《[[開麥拉驚魂|開麥拉驚魂]]》（2008年）的其中一支偽奧斯卡預告片」<ref>{{cite web | last = Walsh | first = Katie | title = Movie review: Not enough suspense in ‘The Finest Hours’ | work = Tribune News Service | url = http://www.duluthnewstribune.com/ae/3934075-movie-review-not-enough-suspense-finest-hours | accessdate = 2016-01-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170325025242/http://www.duluthnewstribune.com/ae/3934075-movie-review-not-enough-suspense-finest-hours | archivedate = 2017-03-25 }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===

截至下檔日，《絕命救援》在美國及加拿大地區共累積了2,760萬美元的票房，加上來自其他地區的2,450萬美元，全球票房共計5,210萬美元，而其製片預算則是8,000萬美元<ref name="BOM"/>。2016年3月，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌報導，迪士尼因該片虧損約7,500萬美元<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rainey |first1=James |title=Disney Expects $75 Million Loss on ‘The Finest Hours’ |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/disney-expects-to-lose-75-million-on-the-finest-hours-1201725537/ |accessdate=2016-03-08 |work=Variety |date=2016-03-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309104843/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/disney-expects-to-lose-75-million-on-the-finest-hours-1201725537/ |archivedate=2016-03-09 }}</ref>。

在北美，電影與《[[功夫熊貓3|功夫熊貓3]]》、《[[格雷的五十道黑影|格雷的五十道黑影]]》及《{{link-en|逆愛 (電影)|Jane Got a Gun|逆愛}}》同期上映並競爭。外界預測，《絕命救援》將在其首映週末透過3,143家電影院進帳1,000萬至1,300萬美元<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/kung-fu-panda-3-finest-hours-fifty-shade-of-black-jane-got-a-gun-box-office-preview-1201691337/ |title=‘Kung Fu Panda 3’ Will Dig Box Office Out Of The Snow With $40M+ Opening – Preview |work=deadline.com |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131093729/http://deadline.com/2016/01/kung-fu-panda-3-finest-hours-fifty-shade-of-black-jane-got-a-gun-box-office-preview-1201691337/ |archivedate=2016-01-31 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=McClintock|first1=Pamela|title=Box Office: 'Kung Fu Panda 3' Trouncing Competition on Friday for $45M Debut|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-kung-fu-panda-860353|accessdate=2016-01-30|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-01-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130103143/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-kung-fu-panda-860353|archivedate=2016-01-30}}</ref>。該片於星期四的午夜場收穫375,000美元，並在首映當天收入330萬美元<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Box Office: Chris Pine’s ‘Finest Hours’ Opens to Choppy $375,000 on Thursday|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/box-office-finest-hours-thursday-opening-1201691667/|accessdate=2016-01-30|work=Variety|date=2016-01-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130084017/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/box-office-finest-hours-thursday-opening-1201691667/|archivedate=2016-01-30}}</ref>。首映週末，《絕命救援》的票房成績為1,030萬美元，排名當週第四<ref name="box office">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/weekend-box-office-kung-fu-panda-3-finest-hours-fifty-shades-of-black-1201692571/ |title=‘Kung Fu Panda 3’ Kicking Up $13M Friday & $44M-$45M Opening Weekend |work=deadline.com |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201063759/http://deadline.com/2016/01/weekend-box-office-kung-fu-panda-3-finest-hours-fifty-shades-of-black-1201692571/ |archivedate=2016-02-01 }}</ref>。

在香港，該片的總票房為870萬[[港元|港幣]]<ref name="香港電影業資料彙編"/>。

